Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.29,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.09,0:00:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎  大小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在呢在呢 親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院內是禁煙的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.35,0:00:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體檢事前調查書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份是警員的  我順便給帶過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.28,0:00:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.57,0:00:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看的仔細點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.74,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們那的警員都是些不讓人省心的料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.50,0:00:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町內會也好 元老院也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.88,0:00:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看來警部的頭也是這麼溫柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們警部的頭可不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.43,0:01:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我們的警員可都是真真切切的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.93,0:01:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟和警察打交道的大多都是人類嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.93,0:01:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  人類逮捕人類是再理所當然的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一旦換成妖怪的話就不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.94,0:01:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我們也沒有町內會和元老院的特殊力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.53,0:01:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然署長是那副模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.12,0:01:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警員也會經常跟著亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要好好看管他們才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.46,0:01:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起老大 聽說町長去旅游了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.25,0:01:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這段時間雄飛會代替小姬去巡邏呢 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 反正我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也要同平常那樣好好巡邏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.64,0:01:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.35,0:01:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉莉拉 莉拉莉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.56,0:01:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 正好來電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.77,0:01:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以回去了吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.53,0:01:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.78,0:01:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會準備好晚餐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滴 就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.68,0:02:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦有了要走進去的動作 就會馬上被改變啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是精神干涉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狂妄啊	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.49,0:02:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下  姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.25,0:02:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術的精髓就在於利用人的心理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不能小看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.67,0:02:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種很強烈的不詳預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面你一直很準呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不希望這麼準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實準
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先掛了 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.15,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 確認情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色的狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.42,0:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要好好的管教下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.38,0:03:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼事 莉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.01,0:03:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是讓獅童去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該早就回到警署了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不可靠的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.90,0:03:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很可靠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在嗶的提示音後留下您的名字和留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和撫子在一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打給她試試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(電話螢幕畫面:火奈 撥號中)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水奈和火奈都不接電話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗婭貝爾小姐也沒有接呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 萊莉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部長的電話？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在回警署的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底要搞多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.05,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底都去做什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.43,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經讀過人類用日本刀和野狗相鬥不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是換成狼的話會是怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我乖乖的待在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.48,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的招數很少見 不是終究是人類 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉啊 我是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我今天狀態不佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到狼說話竟然一點也不驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我從沒有聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上竟有踩著節奏啍著歌的狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能說話已經沒什麼好驚訝的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且你渾身散發著人類的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直接告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.32,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是一隻熊的話可不夠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙竟然敢偷懶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.46,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然結界已經解除那還是收工吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就放過你  已經有了這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見你的時候一定會慢慢享用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得洗白白等著我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很白白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.37,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.81,0:08:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會問你們去幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好會保護的卻失職	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼彌補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在町內會人手不足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果再不好好幹活該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.96,0:09:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 總之先聯繫一下小姬他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.63,0:09:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  白癡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們的話一定會馬上趕回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.01,0:09:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才去休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就由我們自已來解決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我先出去找找線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁豈不是像無頭蒼蠅一般了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他好好冷靜一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時就不用搭理他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.95,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你也捲進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是也帶上我的話 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果火奈有什麼危險的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.84,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 至少現在她還是沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是雙胞胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種事情還是能夠感知到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.64,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她現在沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗你還是先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫雄飛來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.23,0:10:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼進展的話請立刻聯繫我吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  睡箸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也是恢復傷口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有人魚混血才適用的恢復方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.87,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  趁她睡箸了去做個了結吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察全員出動的話應該很快就能找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們目前還不能行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且也沒有署長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣有關妖怪的案件必須要得到署長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直太荒唐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點不荒唐	
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對團體來說老大是重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.65,0:10:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是忠實於老大才能越強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是普通的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要通過團體來增強力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為忠實的警察走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.83,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就快去找署長下命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走狗就該有走狗的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只會等待命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大也有老大的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我們開口了整個集團的力量就會受到影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.55,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這麼多人 都只會等待嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要行動不就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.97,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有別的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.18,0:11:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  工作了 工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉  冷靜點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織是有組織自已的做法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 為什麼非要瞄準那個小鬼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多別的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.04,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是人魚和吸血鬼的混合體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他們的目對就很明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也應該多讀些書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書中有記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.97,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時統治者們世世代代所追求的傳說中的人魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並非是因為數量少而被追捧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人魚體內藏著不老不死的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲得這力量的手段極為簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲血食肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在這樣下去會被吃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那從哪裡開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳？肚子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是整個一下子吞掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很困擾的  中途解除結界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.55,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我好好的幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.98,0:12:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也說過的 力量還不是很穩定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定就要那樣吃掉她嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.82,0:13:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於肉 只有調味後才是美味的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人魚和吸血鬼的混合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上不成熟的肉體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以肉一定會很淡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老不死的力量也很弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要調味的 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.92,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼該怎麼做 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.34,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她放在醬油裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調味是指增強她的妖力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然人魚部分的力量較弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.63,0:13:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要增強吸血鬼的部分來彌補就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.32,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是前途無量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就吃了實在太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你這種程度的血當然是這樣效果了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的的血可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.63,0:14:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與人魚的妖力最吻合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使肉變得美味的是 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人魚之血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那個白色的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓我再跑一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會早點說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.85,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好剛剛還有漏下的看起來美味的肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.28,0:14:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是笑起來更可愛呢	'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說那些沒用的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到自前為止町內還沒有出現任何其他受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還是自覺地較少外出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可城鎮要是陷入緊急狀態怎麼辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.05,0:14:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為警察署實在是靠不住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.09,0:14:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉真是的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.89,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去嗎 德叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去巡邏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  警察署也有自願加入尋找的人吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時巡邏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是字面上的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是火大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們也回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正下班時間早過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在元神召集妖怪獵人的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該見過那傢伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了 當時人那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.84,0:15:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你還知道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.89,0:15:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偽裝成狼的樣子 趁著月色瞄準獵物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的話應該是狼男吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.68,0:15:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼男是夜行性 並且今天又是滿月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓他真是最糟糕的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.47,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼男嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.98,0:16:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.39,0:16:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個妖怪聚集的城鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.48,0:16:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是狼男吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這滿是人類的城鎮裡到底要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不小心說漏嘴吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.08,0:16:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你是要討好人類和他們生活嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這是眾所周知的事實呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮上的居民也都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.83,0:16:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是六角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你們所看的那樣是狼男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得 要一起享用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人魚的肉 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也能和同族一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火奈到底在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是不行了 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯前稍稍運動一下吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉不能接受的表情啊 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.28,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在那悠閒的讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我多讀書的不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.16,0:17:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面或許記錄了狼男的弱點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.66,0:17:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於知識  就算徹夜來看也是無意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.83,0:17:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是 這也是 這本也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.79,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉 快住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正總有一本書裡會有寫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼男的弱點是銀質武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我倒是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是狼男  還有大部分的妖怪弱點就是銀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倉庫裡就有那些裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀之彈什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕快拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.02,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還沒有接到署長的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這到底是搞什麼啊	1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要攻擊我的墨鏡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獅童現在在餐館不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的刀叉倒都是銀質的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也是狼男吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你之前說過警署裡都是真真切切的人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有規定妖怪不能成為警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是至今想成為警察的妖怪幾乎是沒有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算像人類這樣生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為擁有的力量而產生糾紛時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察無論如何還是會袒護人類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就會變成妖怪用槍指著自已的同族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妖怪才不會想變成警察的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點人類不也是一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的同族心理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能想像妖怪們在想些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這樣真的沒有關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然都是狼男處上風的可是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.93,0:19:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相遇的話也許能做個了解結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為長期跟人類在一起變成這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的牙一點都不鋒利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直吃素才變得這麼弱的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼動手  看來你也是餓了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.87,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.33,0:19:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個紅色的 水靈靈的看起來不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美味的喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.48,0:19:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對那孩子動手了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.75,0:20:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過是被滿月的月光照到罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就自認為是變強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.59,0:20:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始蠻得狂妄了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼打不中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.26,0:20:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼事都要講究張弛有度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.39,0:20:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂張與弛 也就是有對比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.43,0:20:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對狼男來說對比就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.57,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿月的光芒和月光下的陰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是狼男就給我好好利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用陰影是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你自己好好想想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.96,0:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用陰影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是說融入夜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話一片漆黑豈不是更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.01,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片漆黑的話  那麼獵物便變得看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的感官反而因此變得靈敏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能導致獵手失去機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來如果不是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵物就會撤底的依靠視覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕而易舉就制眼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也只是一小部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用陰影的方法還有很多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.84,0:21:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.92,0:21:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只是鍍銀不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之前銀彈手槍的話怎麼可能打不中呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.55,0:21:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好槍法阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.47,0:21:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這距離 還敢用那種玩具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.27,0:21:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算是真槍也是打不中我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.69,0:21:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力完全可以應對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.40,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿月帶來的力量嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.98,0:22:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你在尋找的人魚小姑娘現在在警察署吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.70,0:22:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.74,0:22:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著這條街一直走就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.20,0:22:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.33,0:22:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正對手太弱我已經厭倦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.37,0:22:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.75,0:22:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.75,0:22:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於警察的工作都是以結果論成敗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.34,0:22:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然努力了卻沒有結局那便是沒有意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.72,0:22:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不能讓人白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.80,0:22:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的你力量來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.39,0:22:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察署的勝算更大一些吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.06,0:22:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才讓他去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.77,0:22:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我做錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.28,0:22:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.41,0:22:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用怕 我只是留下來看家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.87,0:23:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗了所以不安嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.05,0:23:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.89,0:23:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.47,0:23:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.89,0:23:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗家的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.56,0:23:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是知道的多啊  聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.36,0:23:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸媽媽告訴你的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.48,0:23:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是從大家那裡聽說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.82,0:23:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和水奈已經不記得爸爸媽媽的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.74,0:23:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許你會認識爸爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.75,0:23:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你曾經偶到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的世界裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母是空白世代嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.26,0:23:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止次元的融化 秋名那一代便出發去了那個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.97,0:23:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是那一代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 或許是那一對夫婦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人魚夫婦 我記得哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.23,0:24:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.35,0:24:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是謊言吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.44,0:24:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們既沒有回來  次元融化也沒有停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.74,0:24:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且我也到了這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.66,0:24:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道還不能想像空白世代的處境嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.70,0:24:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.00,0:24:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我根本不瞭解那邊的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.25,0:24:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的世界到底是怎樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.71,0:24:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.46,0:24:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者可以說是只有怨念的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.84,0:24:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許和這個只有妖怪的世界也沒什麼不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.51,0:24:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有來自那個世界的我才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.35,0:24:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有通過我才能了解那個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.44,0:24:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.27,0:24:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以別相信我說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.86,0:24:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是那種說謊不臉紅的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.74,0:24:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.32,0:24:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會引起次元融合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.95,0:24:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道比泉宗家所遭受的待遇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.33,0:25:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了他們報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.95,0:25:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很簡單吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.87,0:25:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你憎恨的是比泉宗家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.13,0:25:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把這世界捲入進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.34,0:25:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.84,0:25:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們什麼瓜葛也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.88,0:25:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界的傢伙又與我有何關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.34,0:25:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 人類會為了比泉宗家的所作所為而痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.39,0:25:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓宗家為此而背上這這份罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.31,0:25:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後不堪罪名的壓迫而匍匐於地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.98,0:25:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定比把他們直接按到在地爽快的多 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.41,0:25:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 可怕的要哭了嘛 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.75,0:25:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.75,0:25:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 話說比泉宗家的往後日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.13,0:25:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  被扭曲成這樣的你好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.60,0:26:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我可憐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.56,0:26:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許同情我 你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.19,0:26:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑你就能理解我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.19,0:26:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我族的憤怒和仇恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.15,0:26:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:25.04,0:26:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.29,0:26:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.37,0:26:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道我為什麼不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.96,0:26:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會覺得你可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.68,0:26:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我變回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.10,0:26:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也懶得等那傢伙回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.19,0:26:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去迎接他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.40,0:26:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為等人來救你會有些意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.19,0:27:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個城鎮看來都是群無用的傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.70,0:27:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
